The legs are both on the left side of the picture. One on the ground and one isn't on the ground.
OK. Which is the fourth picture?

Fourth picture is kind of hard to explain. It has a tilted square at the top in the middle of the picture. Underneath the square is just part of the figure. On the right there are two sharp edges. The left of the picture looks like a half of a giant square.
